import React from 'react'; import './Result.styles.css'; import { useSelector } from 'react-redux'; export default function Result({end}) { const {totalMoves,badMoves} = useSelector((state) => state.movesSlice) let result = (totalMoves-badMoves)/totalMoves*100; return (
Total Moves: {totalMoves}
Bad Moves:{badMoves}
Result: {end? result:}
new game
) }
